{"TopicId":219787,"ForumId":120,"TopicTitle":"Ability to \u0026quot;PAUSE\u0026quot; the game in the VAB","CreatedByName":"Heretic391","CreatedById":66101,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-10-05T02:05:53Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Heretic391","CreatedById":66101,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-10-05T02:05:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo when building in the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E, being able to pause the game would:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\n* Reduce lag (especially in the future with large colonies) so that they won\u0027t be functional.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n* Keep the game on a certain time of day so when you launch your ship, it won\u0027t be night where you can\u0027t see anything.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n* Players can take a break without the game progressing, allowing them to step away from the game without any consequences i.e you could have a ship that\u0027s on its way towards a planets surface but you don\u0027t want it to move yet.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n* Give players more time to plan their spacecraft designs and mission (career mode) strategies without feeling rushed by the game\u2019s progression.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThoughts and suggestions are appreciated.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"mattihase","CreatedById":73161,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-10-05T10:30:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nthank yes!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Aziz","CreatedById":150811,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-10-05T13:27:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow much time are you spending in \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E, exactly? How much does it affect the rest of the game?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224328176\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022219787\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221696471553\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002266101\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Heretic391\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n11 hours ago, Heretic391 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nyou could have a ship that\u0027s on its way towards a planets surface but you don\u0027t want it to move yet.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou know, having that and doing literally anything else than taking control would be just dumb. So what, you finish the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E work, hit the launchpad and... switch to reentering ship immediately? You may as well start the construction after landing.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HephaistosFnord","CreatedById":227537,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-10-15T20:18:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPause and/or timewarp, with a clock somewhere. I would love to be able to timewarp to dawn *before* I hit the runway, since many of my planes bounce around like crazy on the runway, preventing timewarping.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Royalswissarmyknife","CreatedById":216092,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-10-15T20:19:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224328258\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022219787\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221696512462\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022150811\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022The Aziz\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 10/5/2023 at 9:27 AM, The Aziz said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow much time are you spending in \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E, exactly?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou dont want to know.\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:/\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/ZNGIcon1.png\u0022 title=\u0022:/\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DibzNr","CreatedById":212219,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-10-24T08:31:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224330453\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022219787\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221697401198\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022216092\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Royalswissarmyknife\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 10/15/2023 at 9:19 PM, Royalswissarmyknife said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou dont want to know.\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:/\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/ZNGIcon1.png\u0022 title=\u0022:/\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMe leaving my game AFK for 8 hours straight\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Filed.Teeth","CreatedById":178610,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-10-28T07:12:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI always thought time suspended when you in the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E in KSP1, is it different in KSP2?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n(And was I wrong about that in 1, lol?)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-10-28T08:09:57Z\u0022 title=\u002210/28/2023 08:09  AM\u0022 data-short=\u0022Oct 28\u0022\u003EOctober 28, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by Filed.Teeth\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Filed.Teeth","CreatedById":178610,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-10-28T08:09:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224323965\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022219497\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221695211350\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022149515\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Lyneira\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 9/20/2023 at 2:02 AM, Lyneira said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn KSP2, time\u00A0doesn\u0027t pause while you\u0027re in the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027d also be curious if in an OAB which is open to space, we\u0027ll get to see Kerbin or another planet passing by below us as we orbit it. I hope so, at least.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFound my own answer elsewhere lol.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo definite thumbs up on this proposal.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-10-28T08:10:51Z\u0022 title=\u002210/28/2023 08:10  AM\u0022 data-short=\u0022Oct 28\u0022\u003EOctober 28, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by Filed.Teeth\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"dansiegel30","CreatedById":225462,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-10-28T11:28:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI thought it was naturally paused until I left the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E, and it was dark outside my house, and it was dark when I tried to launch.\u00A0 I\u0027m ok with them leaving it realtime, but a pause option would be nice...especially one day when there is SO much going on in the Kerbol system such as having multiple colonies, dozens of craft in orbit...they certainly dont want the CPU eating up realtime on that while you are in the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E - in fact, that just happened to me...the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E was dropping down to sub-10 FPS when it had been perfect for the last few days while on 0.1.5 - turned out it was a crashed rover I left on the Mun, which was shaking and wobbling radically, eating up performace.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Bej Kerman","CreatedById":182413,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-10-28T11:50:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224328258\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022219787\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221696512462\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022150811\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022The Aziz\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 10/5/2023 at 2:27 PM, The Aziz said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow much time are you spending in \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E, exactly? How much does it affect the rest of the game?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat\u0027s not the only reason they gave;\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224328176\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022219787\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221696471553\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002266101\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Heretic391\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 10/5/2023 at 3:05 AM, Heretic391 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n* Reduce lag (especially in the future with large colonies) so that they won\u0027t be functional.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n"}]}